    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Transparent devices often of gelatin or glass which are placed in front of a light source and serve to diminish the intensity or alter the color of the light.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
